The paper discusses the trade-off between performance and cost in the context of Infrastructure as a Service (IaaS), which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of FPGAs and GPUs also suggests a focus on computer architecture (cs.AR). The paper also discusses optimization techniques, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the use of multiple platforms and the need to allocate tasks suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY).
